subject: Annouce: Version 1.1 of dbunit testing framework released!!!
msgSnippet: Version 1.1 just been released. This version includes better connection management and performance improvement. Feedbacks are welcome and much appreciated.
messageBody:
Version 1.1 just been released. This version includes better connection
management and performance improvement.

Feedbacks are welcome and much appreciated.
